openapi: 3.0.0
tags:
  - name: storage
    description: named set storage api
paths:

      tags:
        - storage
      parameters:
        - name: idType
          in: query
          required: false
          description: limit list to the given idType
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful response

            application/json:

                title: list of namedsets
                type: array
                items:
                  $ref: '#/components/schemas/namedset'

        '404':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/notFound'

      x-swagger-router-controller: tdp_core

            schema:

          application/x-www-form-urlencoded:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/namedset'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                title: list of namedsets
                type: array
                items:
                  $ref: '#/components/schemas/namedset'
        '403':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/notAllowed'
        '404':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/notFound'
  '/storage/namedsets/{namedset}':

      operationId: storage.get_namedset
      description: get a dataset
      tags:
        - storage
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful response

        '403':

        '404':

    delete:

      tags:
        - storage
      responses:
        '200':

            application/json:

                title: number of removed entries
                type: integer
        '403':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/notAllowed'
        '404':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/notFound'

        '403':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/notAllowed'
        '404':

   post:

        subTypeKey:
          type: string
        subTypeValue:

      required:

        - type
        - creator
        - permissions
        - description
        - idType
        - ids
        - subTypeKey
        - subTypeValue
    attachment:
      type: object
      additionalProperties: true
